snippet.title: Interplanetary Release Trailer [Turn-Based Artillery Strategy for PC, Mac and Linux]
snippet.description:
Steam:         http://store.steampowered.com/app/278910
Website:       http://www.interplanetarygame.com
Facebook:     https://www.facebook.com/teamjollyroger
Twitter:          https://twitter.com/teamjollyroger

Interplanetary is a gravitational artillery strategy game, where players wage wars by developing their home planets and firing their planetary barrages.

Releasing out of Steam Early Access on May 12th, 2015. Available on Windows, Mac and Linux.
